channels.name: image-jams
channels.topic:
**Welcome to our image-jam forum!**
This is an experimental space where anyone can create 'themed' or 'collaborative' image threads where anyone can post things in-spirit with the original post. Please be nice, please stay in theme and have fun!

üîπ** 1. Search first:** It's likely there's already an existing thread about your theme. Come join us there!
üîπ** 2.  Make new threads search-friendly.** If you make a new thread, model your title after existing thread titles for clarity, and include helpful keywords so others can find it easily. (Emoji not required, but appreciated. Discord makes them annoying to add though.) 
üîπ** 3. Stay on theme.**

channels.name: üß™meta-testing
channels.topic:
The purpose of this channel is to research, discuss and test potential metas of any kind, before publishing them in #meta-publication. Stumbled upon something potentially useful while playing or researching, but it is not quite ready yet for publication? This channel is the perfect place to research it publicly, alone or together.

You should select at least one tag when creating posts. These are the possible tags:

**Infrastructure**: Post designed to map the style of traffic signs, bollards, utility poles, road lines, stickers, trash cans, pavement, etc.
**Landscape**: Post intended to map plants, terrain types, agriculture, etc.
**Architecture**: Post designed to map the style of buildings, windows, roofs, etc.
**Miscellaneous**: Everything that doesn't fit in one of the aforementioned categories, such as language and culture, car and coverage metas, etc. Feel free to also use this tag to make posts about meta research in general.
**Docs contribution**: Forum post intended to give feedback to a doc maker to improve or expand their document.

channels.name: bug-reporting-forum
channels.topic:
The Bug-Report forum is a place to report issues that you experience while playing Fortnite. 
Due to the scope of Fortnite, we can only accept reports for issues in: 
- Battle Royale including Ranked and Tournaments 
-  OG Fortnite 
-  Fortnite Reload 
-  Ballistic
### For all other modes: consult #how-to-report-bugs 

## Please check for existing threads about the issue you are experiencing before posting. 
If there is already one, add your information there. Feel free to share potential solutions and workarounds to what you're experiencing. 

## This forum is not a substitute for EPIC Games Player Support. 
- We will not respond to each thread here: 
  - Do not post expecting a resolution or immediate response. 
- Billing and Account specific issues cannot be processed within Discord: 
To open a ticket with Player Support, visit: <https://fn.gg/support>

## Instructions & Rules:
Before you create a new post, check that a similar post doesn't already exists for the same issue. If you need detailed instructions, including a visual guide: #how-to-report-bugs

If no other post already exists, click "New Post" at the top of this window.

üìù Make sure to add as much information about the issue as you can. You must select at least one TAG before submitted a post. Additional details such as **platform**, **region**, **error message**, **frequency**, **expected outcome** and **step by step process to reproduce (if applicable)** can be useful details to include.

We allow members to upload relevant screenshots or short videos to their posts. 
**No External Links:  Please upload directly**

If there's already an existing post about your problem, please add your experience to that post instead of making a new one. We're more likely to notice an active thread with relevant information. 

‚ùó Be mindful of what you are sharing, ensure anything that you post doesn't include personal information, account details, or billing details. 

‚ö†Ô∏è ### Scammers Operate Here
Be watching for fake accounts posing as Support Agents. Official Server Staff and EPIC Games Staff will have a relevant role. 

They will never ask for your password and will never redirect you to another support server on Discord nor ask you to sent an email. 

If in doubt, only use the official player support link provided above.
